snippet.title: CINEMA - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3144070/CINEMA

CINEMA: A groundbreaking thriller that puts time manipulation in your hands. Inspired by classic silent films, you'll navigate multiple timelines, alter cause and effect, and craft your own path through a gripping narrative. Every decision ripples through time – are you ready to play?

Developed by Trinity Team
